</section>

<section class="connect">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Connect</h2>
    <p class="details">Meet our e-senseis! Your personal e-sensei will guide you on a step-by-step basis with weekly emails, monthly phone calls, and specific reminders to keep you on the right track as you grow your business.</p>

    <div class="senseis">
      <div class="sensei">
