</section>

<section class="community">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Community</h2>
    <p class="details">Join a growing community of location-independent professionals! As you test at higher levels you will be rewarded with personalized assessments and you will gain exclusive contacts to top-level senseis not available to white belts. E-Sensei is not just another social network or another place to post your resume, but a networking tool that you can use to prove yourself and gain respect in a competitive arena.</p>
